channel.title: Project fubregen clietn v6
channel.description:
Hello everyone. before you start flaming me about this. fubergen (sir roju) has gave me permission to post this client for you all.
here is a list of the updates me and sir roju have made for this new client
we have added a switch tab into the Toolbar. it only switches your spellbook from modern to ancients. and from ancients to modern new client background. hope you like it we have removed the substance theme to make the client more stable. we have made the client compatible with deltascape items. noclip has been removed from the extra tab in Jframe
here are a few pictures of the client. NOTE: the client does not automatically connect to any server.
now for the download link
http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?m1nmz2zzrht
now for the credits
Credits: Most thanks goes for Danno Fubergen for letting me work on his clients with him. i luv u man. me (dan) for helping perfect a few things in the client Galkon for models, that i added SilentCJ for new d plate, and his novelty weapons Ricscape client v8.5's factors Background created byIPhoenix Java tutorial from java Cocoa Enurscape For server's selection codes [modified for client ] Danno - Most New jframe features from dannos client [i just non renamed them and modified for my client]
« Last Edit: February 12, 2009, 03:53:08 am by k0ed u »
